title: Introduction to meanings of artists, albums, songs and playlists
answer:
Artist: Classified by the singer, and songs belonging to the same singer are placed in a directory. 

 Album: Classified by the album title, and songs in the same album are placed in a directory. 

 Songs: Sorted by naming rules and stored in a large directory. 

 Playlist: You can set up a custom list to add your favorite music files to it.
